<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Southview</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in 1950, Southview is one of the oldest communities located in the South-East quadrant of Calgary.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The last community to be developed inside the Greater Forest Lawn Area, Southview is also a part of the International Avenue Business Revitalization Zone and is represented by the Ward 10 Councilor in the Calgary City Council.</p>

            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Southview include single-family detached homes, bungalows and apartment condominiums that are typically listed at an average price of $350,000.</p>
        </div>
